Allen & Unwin:
Company HQ - Crows Nest, New South Wales, Australia
Founding Date - August 1914
Current CEO - Robert Gorman
Listed Imprints - Arena, Crows Nest, House of Books, Inspired Living, Murdoch Books
Notable Awards - Publisher of the Year, Prime Minister's Award for Children's Fiction

Simon & Schuster:
Company HQ - New York City, New York, United States
Founding Date - January 1924
Current CEO - Carolyn Reidy
Listed Imprints - Adams Media, Gallery Books Group, Scribner, Atria, Aladdin, Little Simon
Notable Awards - Nobel Prize for Literature, Pulitzer Prize, National Book Award

Penguin Random House:
Company HQ - New York City, New York, United States
Founding Date - July 2013
Current CEO - Markus Dohle
Listed Imprints - Dorling Kindersley, Crown Publishing Group, Knopf Doubleday, Penguin Publishing
Notable Awards - National Book Critics Circle Award, #1 New York Times Bestseller, Nobel Peace Prize
